text: Every year @FedEx is supposed to deliver my new iPhone and every year I have issues with FedEx. 7:38pm and still no package.

@jdfwarrior Hello David, this is Rochelle. I am very sorry your package has not been delivered. Would you like me to look into this for you?  Please verify your full name, address, tracking number, phone number and email address. 
Thank you.

@FedExHelp I’ve already called 2-3 times today and was gauranteed numerous times it would be here by 8, which, it wasn’t. So, I don’t want to go through that whole spiel again.  It’s just going to make me more mad than I already am.

@ngocphamm @Apple @FedEx @tim_cook Well my thing is too though, if I wanted to drive to the local and office and pick it up, what’s the point in someone paying for delivery?! If I wanted to drive somewhere to get it, I would have gone to the Apple Store today instead of preordering
